description: Too Cold for Training ? It might be hot in the Northern hemisphere but down in Sydney Australia it's the middle of winter. Nat Summers and Andy are feeling the cold. The coach is unrelenting and the guys are pissed! So they do what seems sensible and heat each other up! In fact warm turns to torrid as Nat gives Andy the pounding of his life in a city-scape fuck-scene guaranteed to make you just as hot!
title: Cum On Aussie, Scene #03
